description.narrative: An integrated programme to promote Kafala and to align alternative care to United Nation (UN) guidelines was developed and adopted by the inter-ministerial commission in charge of the implementation of policies and action plans for children. The programme offers a great opportunity to reform the system of Kafala, to prevent unnecessary separation of children from their families and to ensure quality and appropriate alternative arrangements for children without parental care. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:14/01/2022
